    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered here is an investment-grade E36 M3 in concours-level condition. This specimen features the S50 inline-six powerplant, delivering linear torque across the rev range with a flawlessly maintained VANOS variable valve timing system. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise ZF 5-speed manual transmission and a factory 3.15 limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal power delivery. The chassis remains factory-straight with zero subframe fatigue, riding on a refreshed suspension geometry featuring Bilstein B8 dampers and OEM bushings. The exterior retains its factory depth and luster, while the interior 'Vader' seats remain supple with no bolster wear. Mechanically synchronized and aesthetically peerless, this is a turn-key example for the discerning collector.",
